Company History

Company History


Major Changes and Trends for Major Product Development



1948
Marusho Industrial Co., Ltd. was established
						




Developed such original products based on its formulation
								and coating technique as (to ‘55):
Slime-control agents
Epoxy resins for electrical insulation
Engineering / drafting films, diazo-sensitized second original films
 







1956
Established a laboratory in Adachi Ward, Tokyo.



1962
The laboratory was separated, then established independently as Somar
							Manufacturing Co., Ltd.
							

Promoted fine patterning technology and developed such products
									for PCB industry as (to ‘75):
Electron beam resists for semiconductors
Resist inks for PCBs
SMT adhesives





1984
Merged with Somar Manufacturing Co., Ltd. and company name has been
							changed to SOMAR Corporation.



1985
Was registered at the over-the-counter stock market of Japan Securities
							Dealers Association.



1988
Has been listed on Second Section of Tokyo Stock Exchange.
							

Introduced such various functional films that would adapt
									to the needs arose from new technical trend as (to ’89):
Films for ink-jet printing
Non-reflective light shading black films for optical instruments
Adhesive films for FPC production processes 





1995
Gained ISO9001 certification of quality management (now being applied
							across the company)



2001
Soka Factory gained ISO14001 certification of environmental management.

Strengthened such business for joint-development, contract
									production/OEM, etc. as (‘00 to ’02):
Electro-magnetic wave shielding adhesive films
Metal foil coating 
Thermal expansion films for electronic parts production processes 





2006
Established Somar Corporation (H.K.) Ltd. (Hong Kong）




2007
Established Somar Fine Chemicals (Zhuhai) Ltd.（Zhuhai, Guangdong, China）




2008
Established SOMATECH Corp.（Sendai, Miyagi, Japan）
Established Somar (Taiwan) Co., Ltd.（Chungho, Taipei, Taiwan）
Established Siam Somar Co., Ltd.（Bangkok, Thailand）



2010
Established Somar Fine Chemicals (Zhuhai) Ltd. Shanghai Branch(Shanghai, China)



 



