Somar International Ltd.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 4:40 PM ET
Electrical Equipment

Company Overview of Somar International Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Somar International, Ltd. provides energy management products. The company offers Powerboss that adjusts power to a motor as per the load changes, and monitors the motor's load and calculates the amount of power required. Its products are used in various applications, such as compressors, refrigeration, air conditioning, air handling, escalators, presses, conveyors, plastic injection moulding machines, die cast machines, hydraulics, sheet bending machines, crushers, granulators, milling machines, pulping machines, saws, cutting machines, sewing machines, slurry pumps, and variable viscosity pumps. The company offers its products through a network of distributors. Somar International, Ltd. wa...
Somar International, Ltd. provides energy management products. The company offers Powerboss that adjusts power to a motor as per the load changes, and monitors the motor's load and calculates the amount of power required. Its products are used in various applications, such as compressors, refrigeration, air conditioning, air handling, escalators, presses, conveyors, plastic injection moulding machines, die cast machines, hydraulics, sheet bending machines, crushers, granulators, milling machines, pulping machines, saws, cutting machines, sewing machines, slurry pumps, and variable viscosity pumps. The company offers its products through a network of distributors. Somar International, Ltd. was founded in 1991 and is based in Truro, the United Kingdom. As of March 24, 2012, Somar International Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Mark Group Limited.
